-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Nguy%E1%BB%87t-Thi%C3%AAn-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-thu-k%E1%BB%B3-c%E1%BA%ADn/poem-l6vi0z0gZmrHgxG_hz8eCw">Nguyệt (Thiên thượng thu kỳ cận) - 月（天上秋期近）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%81u-B%E1%BB%95-Chi/Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nghi-o%C3%A1n/poem-GRSSI-PHn8LOX_d2OAWzMA">Phương Nghi oán - 芳儀怨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%81u-B%E1%BB%95-Chi/author-sHoO5f0MU0Lsfjb4PEm2vg">Triều Bổ Chi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/T%E1%BB%91-trung-t%C3%ACnh/poem-EfNc8fssq4nwf0WjqNOWdA">Tố trung tình - 訴衷情</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%E1%BA%B1ng/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-s%E1%BB%AD-thi-Bi%E1%BB%87n-thu%E1%BB%B7/poem-GdkWui7Y4fiXRiCgi3P2ww">Vịnh sử thi - Biện thuỷ - 詠史詩－汴水</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%E1%BA%B1ng/author-QGyhycNQKN2UVF9H-N6Zaw">Hồ Tằng</a>)<br></div>	</div>
